comments.body:
{code}
+    DAG dag = (DAG) info;
{code}
is a giant hack, and can break in the future if Tez implements DagInfo in a different way.

May be better to modify Tez to expose the relevant information via DagInfo, rather than casting to DAG which is an internal structure to Tez.
Relevant jira on the Tez side: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-3770
